XTUPLE DATABASE
===============

This repository contains the database object definitions that enable a standard xTuple database to run in conjunction with the xTuple node based Datasource (https://github.com/xtuple/datasource).

Prerequisites
-------------
 * [PostgreSQL] (http://www.postgresql.org/) -- 'v9.1.0+'
 * [plV8js] (http://code.google.com/p/plv8js/wiki/PLV8)
 * [Postbooks] (http://sourceforge.net/projects/postbooks) -- 'v3.8.0+'

Instructions
------------

* 'cd postgresql'
*  psql -d [database] -U [user] -f 'init_script.sql'
